post_text:
"Coming together is a beginning;
keeping together is progress;
working together is success."
- Henry Ford

At BPCS, we go above and beyond academic rigor to ensure that each student feels s/he has a place and a voice in our small school. To wit, this past Friday, our entire 8th grade class went out to Prospect Park to play games, bond with teachers, and build an authentic sense of community both in and outside of the classroom. It looking like a great start to the school year!

